      "role": "user",
      "content": "I get that it's all discredited now, but for my essay i need to be specific about the actual claims they made. Like, instead of just saying they thought some were \"superior,\" what were the specific criteria they used to rank different groups? What were the actual \"scientific\" distinctions they pointed to between, say, Northern Europeans and other groups? I want to make sure I can describe their specific logic accurately without just using general terms.",
